  m_sTitle "End Conditions"
  m_sTextData "AFRF 85% casualty rate: Rebel major victory"\
  ""\
  "70 mins pass with no conclusion: Rebel minor victory"\
  ""\
  "AFRF takes control of both objectives: AFRF victory"\
  ""\
