 Russia1main {
  coords 7162.79 17.844 2852.156
  m_sTitle "Brief"
  m_sTextData "<h1><b><u>Friendly</h1></b></u>"\
  "Friendly forces are, at most, a company (-) of Russian infantry with 2x BMPs. Your mission is to take South Side and North Side; kill all Rebels you encounter. If you make up 90% of the population in an objective, you take it."\
  ""\
  "<h1><b><u>Enemy</h1></b></u>"\
  "The enemy is, at most, 41 anti-Assad rebel fighters. There're probably some ISIS terrorists in the mix, too, so don't feel too bad. They will likely conduct a delaying action at the first objective, using RPGs and small arms to ambush and then fallback (if they're smart). Expect to encounter AT mines."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_AFRF"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
