 INSURGENT1main {
  coords 6383.345 17.844 3004.857
  angles 0 -38.5 0
  m_sTitle "Brief"
  m_sTextData "<h1><b><u>Friendly</h1></b></u>"\
  "Friendly forces are, at most, 41 anti-Assad rebel fighters. The overarching plan is to conduct a delaying action using RPGs and small arms to ambush and then fallback. It would be wise not to over-commit to defending the southern objective area. By spawn, there are 4x sedans and 2x Ural trucks to be used for transportation. Each Ural truck has 8x AT mines."\
  ""\
  "<h1><b><u>Enemy</h1></b></u>"\
  "The enemy is, at most, a company (-) of Russian infantry with 2x BMPs. They are attempting to push us back further into the city. Their approach options are limited due to excessive mines and the urban environment. We expect them to take control of the 2x marked objective areas. If they make up 90% of the population in an objective area, it will be captured."\
  ""\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_INSURGENT"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
